  "id": "RAW_1e5d5124",
  "title": "管你模型多大，250 份有毒文档统统放倒，Anthropic：LLM 比想象中脆弱",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2650994693&idx=1&sn=44f616fa0667abad9e4a036d19d2266b",
  "date": "2025-10-10 03:45:00",
